        "endTime": 62274,
        "slowStartTime": 87645,
        "slowEndTime": 93636
    },
    {
        "text": "The brothers died two years apart.",
        "startTime": 62809,
        "endTime": 64627,
        "slowStartTime": 94363,
        "slowEndTime": 97165
    },
    {
        "text": "They are buried at opposite ends of the village graveyard,...",
