        "endTime": 67968,
        "slowStartTime": 97392,
        "slowEndTime": 102177
    },
    {
        "text": "...proof that even in death there remained a great bitter divide between them.",
        "startTime": 68126,
        "endTime": 72118,
        "slowStartTime": 102339,
        "slowEndTime": 108402
    },
    {
        "text": "And so it was for decades until 2009.",
